packages.description:
NOV Chart
An advanced charting control for .NET, covering a vast feature set of charting types for presentational, 
business, scientific, financial, real-time monitoring, statistical and other types of applications. 

For more information visit:
https://www.nevron.com/products-open-vision-nov-chart-control-overview.aspx

Documentation available at:
http://helpopenvision.nevron.com/
